[I] A library and command-line tools for Diff & Patch between binaries

[T] A C/C++ library and command-line tools for Diff & Patch between binary
[T] files or directories; cross-platform; runs fast; create small
[T] delta/differential; support large files and limit memory requires when
[T] diff & patch.

[U] https://github.com/sisong/HDiffPatch

[A] sisong
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] MIT
[V] 5.1.0

[D] 9ca99e23dd34937d8128d81d56a863b9dd4b44db760d0dee991d1938 HDiffPatch-5.1.0.tar.gz https://github.com/sisong/HDiffPatch/archive/v5.1.0/

var_append makeopt ' ' 'LDEF=0 LZMA=0 ZSTD=0 MD5=0 XXH=0'
var_append makeinstopt ' ' 'LDEF=0 LZMA=0 ZSTD=0 MD5=0 XXH=0 INSTALL_BIN=$root$bindir'
